'''約翰·菲利普·「皮魯」·艾斯貝克'''（{{lang-da|Johan Philip "Pilou" Asbæk}}，{{IPA-da|pʰiˈluː ˈæːsb̥ɛɡ̊}}，{{bd|1982年|3月2日}}）是一位[[丹麥|丹麥]]男演員。較著名的是丹麥政治電視劇《{{link-en|權力的堡壘|Borgen (TV series)}}》（2010年至2013年）中飾演[[政治化妝師|政治化妝師]]卡斯帕·尤爾（Kasper Juul）<ref name=Indepedent-Borgen-2013>{{cite news|last1=Mesure|first1=Susie|title=Fancy a Danish? What about Pilou Asbaek - the man who plays Kasper Juul in ‘Borgen’|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/fancy-a-danish-what-about-pilou-asbaek--the-man-who-plays-kasper-juul-in-borgen-8603842.html|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2013-05-04|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925014737/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/fancy-a-danish-what-about-pilou-asbaek--the-man-who-plays-kasper-juul-in-borgen-8603842.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年，艾斯貝克贏得[[柏林國際影展|柏林國際影展]]的[[流星獎|流星獎]]<ref name=HReporter-Berlinale-ShootingStars-2011>{{cite news|last1=Kastelan|first1=Karsten|title=Shooting Stars Initiative Showcases Rising European Stars at Berlinale|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shooting-stars-initiative-showcases-rising-99211|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2011-02-13|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308004957/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shooting-stars-initiative-showcases-rising-99211|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年又贏得了[[奧雅納斯普羅格獎|奧雅納斯普羅格獎]]<ref name=Politiken-OveSprogøe-2012>{{cite news|last1=Bergløv|first1=Emil|title=Pilou Asbæk vinder Ove Sprogøe Prisen|url=https://politiken.dk/kultur/filmogtv/ECE1845354/pilou-asbaek-vinder-ove-sprogoee-prisen/|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[Politiken|Politiken]]|date=2012-12-17|archive-date=2016-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526044725/http://politiken.dk/kultur/filmogtv/ECE1845354/pilou-asbaek-vinder-ove-sprogoee-prisen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早期生活==
艾斯貝克出生於[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]，母親Maria Patricia（娘家姓Tonn）和父親Jacob A. Asbæk一同在哥本哈根經營著畫廊<ref name=BigIssue-Art-NotInvestment-2015>{{cite news|title=Pilou Asbæk: Buy Art to Look At: Not As An Investment|url=http://www.bigissue.com/features/interviews/5374/pilou-asb-k-buy-art-to-look-at-not-as-an-investment|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[The_Big_Issue|The Big Issue]]|date=2015-06-18|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104010803/http://www.bigissue.com/features/interviews/5374/pilou-asb-k-buy-art-to-look-at-not-as-an-investment|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他的母親出生於[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的[[卡薩布蘭卡|卡薩布蘭卡]]，父親是丹麥人，而母親是法國人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kvinfo.dk/side/597/bio/1068/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-02-20 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104005209/http://www.kvinfo.dk/side/597/bio/1068/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Haaretz-Borgen-2013>{{cite news|last1=Kupfer|first1=Ruta|title='Mad Men' of Northern Europe|url=http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/magazine/mad-men-of-northern-europe.premium-1.496177|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]|date=2013-01-24|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924235903/http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/magazine/mad-men-of-northern-europe.premium-1.496177|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親來自丹麥的[[哈默爾|哈默爾]]<ref name=Scotsman-Hijacking-2013>{{cite news|last1=Synnot|first1=Siobhan|title=Borgen’s Pilou Asbaek on his Somalian pirate film|url=http://www.scotsman.com/what-s-on/film/borgen-s-pilou-asbaek-on-his-somalian-pirate-film-1-2926468|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[The_Scotsman|The Scotsman]]|date=2013-05-11|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924160040/http://www.scotsman.com/what-s-on/film/borgen-s-pilou-asbaek-on-his-somalian-pirate-film-1-2926468|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他有兩個哥哥，其中一個Thomas Asbæk為Asbæk藝術諮詢公司的藝術顧問，另一位Martin Asbæk則是Martin Asbæk畫廊的老闆<ref name=Eurowoman-BrothersAsbaek-2012>{{cite news|last1=Knutzen|first1=Susanne|title=Kom tæt på brødrene Asbæk|url=http://www.eurowoman.dk/fra-magasinet/kom-tat-pa-brodrene-asbak/|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=Eurowoman|date=2012-11-05|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630051043/http://www.eurowoman.dk/fra-magasinet/kom-tat-pa-brodrene-asbak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他曾就讀寄宿學校[[郝魯鄉學校|郝魯鄉學校]]，在那學習電視劇的製作<ref name=Berlingske-SexDrugsTaxes-2013>{{cite news|last1=Zøllner|first1=Kristoffer|title=Pilou Asbæk: Det er jo bare skuespil|url=http://www.b.dk/personlig-udvikling/pilou-asbaek-det-er-jo-bare-skuespil|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=[[Berlingske|Berlingske]]|date=2013-08-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924125352/http://www.b.dk/personlig-udvikling/pilou-asbaek-det-er-jo-bare-skuespil|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾斯貝克於2008年從[[丹麥全國戲劇和當代舞蹈學校|丹麥全國戲劇學校]]畢業<ref name=Scotsman-Hijacking-2013 />。

